title: Warriors Are An Iconic Dynasty
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss the Warriors place in NBA history. Where do they rank amongst the all-time NBA dynasties. Now that Steph Curry has his Finals MVP – what does that mean for his legacy? PLUS, what happened to Jayson Tatum in Game 6? The Celtics collapsed, do we expect to see this group back in the Finals? All that and more.
